snippet.title: Michael Anderson - HL2: Outpost 16
snippet.description:
http://www.mikeadesign.com
Outpost 16 is a single player modification for Half-Life 2 I created by myself over the period of 6 months. It's the first level I ever made and required custom animation, voice over, textures, and models.

Music mixed from: Datsik, There Will Be Blood soundtrack, Children of Men soundrack, and The Thin Red Line soundtrack.
